snippet.title: Half-Life 2: Survivor Ver2.0 - Battle Mode Gameplay
snippet.description:
Gameplay footage of Battle Mode with bots in Half-Life 2: Survivor Ver2.0 played on the PC. Actual gameplay begins at 1:40.

Endless gratitude goes to ben1066 for fixing the binaries. Your generosity will not be forgotten through all eternity.
